{"tid":1209513,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"齊齊搭港鐵集中區","createTime":"2019-06-12T11:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T12:01:58.000Z","uid":156096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca61a181f047b89afe3f00ee400013d1ac760e2","tid":1209513,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:38:15.000Z","msg":"依家出面有示威行動，聽日搭巴士極有可能會大塞車。<br />\n為保大家能夠準時返工返學，聽日大家應該要早啲起身搭港鐵。<br />\n由於可能搭車人數會眾多，有機會逼爆每架地鐵，大家可以帶埋櫈去，有機會有排企。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等得太耐嘅人士(包括總站/非總站) 可以喺各個地鐵站嘅入閘機前同出入口，同想入站既&lt;打工仔&gt;講聲已經地鐵逼爆，叫佢地搭巴士，以免有&lt;打工仔&gt;入咗閘，但係上唔到地鐵，引發任何衝突。<br />\n我希望大家能夠透過各個途徑(facebook,whatsapp, ig等)，鼓勵身邊既朋友/家人聽日提早搭地鐵。<br />\n下面網止列出各路線首班車時間:<br />\n&lt;url&gt;<a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/services/service_hours_search.php?query_type=search&amp;station=83&lt;/url&gt;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fservices%2Fservice_hours_search.php%3Fquery_type%3Dsearch%26station%3D83%3C%2Furl%3E&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=a12799cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/services/service_hours_search.php?query_type=search&amp;station=83&lt;/url&gt;</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁多位和理非非嘅打工仔或者學生，你地係時間要盡自己責任，聽日提早搭車返工返學，唔好遲到。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ffa46d8ffc0f8c5a078b396e37d75451aaf487","tid":1209513,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"石禮謙話畀大家知，香港人最緊張嘅係經濟<br />\n<br />\n講個知識畀大家知<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">每塞6分鐘車，就會有28億損失</span></span><br />\n<br />\n舊Source： <a href=\"https://www.master-insight.com/塞車造成多少經濟損失？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.master-insight.com%2F%E5%A1%9E%E8%BB%8A%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=NZQUy3Ple5Igpjs